_sText:
Since the map is greater than 16mb it wont work on your server unless you add this in your server.cfg file.

net_maxfilesize 64

the '64' stands for file size in MB. The max is 64. If that doesn't work try...

sv_allowupload 1 
sv_allowdownload 1 



Make sure to put sv_airaccelerate to at least 200 and there is a little bit of surf
AND A WORKING TRAMPOLINE YAY
